version_description:
Improvements in this version:
1) Some friendly tips added.
2) Show Feed page when opening app.
3) improve Direct Message video and photo qualities.
4) Add a switch of autoplay feature.
5) Show Downloading progress page when downloading videos.
6) Feature of copying description of Direct Message.

This app has been updated by Apple to use the latest Apple signing certificate.

Bug fixed and performance improved.
